               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I was in very great distress—the man could ears 30<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a week, and sometimes did not bring me 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I thought of getting them out again.</p>
